  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">The book titled \"Research-Based Perspectives on the Psychophysiology of Yoga,\" published by IGI Global in 2018, has generated a noteworthy scholarly uptake, with 12 citations recorded to date, reflecting its relevance in academic discussions surrounding the psychophysiological effects of yoga.</p>\n\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Published in 2018, \"Research-Based Perspectives on the Psychophysiology of Yoga\" has established a significant academic footprint, achieving 12 citations. This level of scholarly uptake underscores its relevance in advancing the understanding of how yoga impacts mental and physiological health, making it a valuable resource for researchers and practitioners alike.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">The book offers comprehensive insights into the integration of research and practice in yoga, contributing to an evolving discourse in the fields of psychology and physiology. While there are currently no documented public discussions or mentions on platforms such as Wikipedia or Reddit, the established citations suggest that it is being referenced in academic circles, affirming its scholarly impact.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">The strength of this work lies in its commercial linkages, evidenced by its presence on platforms like Amazon and Goodreads. Such commercial visibility not only enhances its accessibility but also indicates an ongoing interest in the subject matter among broader audiences. This engagement is critical as it translates academic insights into practical applications that can benefit public health.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">Despite the absence of various community discourse indicators and online presence data, the book\u2019s contributions are vital in fostering discussions around yoga's psychophysiological benefits. The alignment with sustainability goals, reflected in its notation of being linked to one Sustainable Development Goal, indicates a commitment to addressing important contemporary issues through research. As such, it serves as a foundational text for further research in the psychophysiological dimensions of yoga, poised for future engagement and exploration within both academic and practical contexts.</p>",
